WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.750
Hey, good morning, family. How are y'all

00:00:02.760 --> 00:00:04.990
doing today? Well, we're going to do

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.230
another prayer video, so I hope

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:11.549
y'all are ready. In the last video,

00:00:11.559 --> 00:00:14.190
I think it went pretty well for

00:00:14.190 --> 00:00:14.200
not having

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:15.709
done one of those in

00:00:15.719 --> 00:00:19.150
a while, but thank you for joining me.

00:00:19.150 --> 00:00:19.160
To

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:21.230
those that have watched the

00:00:21.240 --> 00:00:23.349
last one and want to pray again today,

00:00:23.359 --> 00:00:26.029
thank you again for joining me.

00:00:26.039 --> 00:00:28.710
This would be video number two.

00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:30.230
I'm going to go over the things

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:32.630
that the Lord showed me in prayer

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:34.510
yesterday, what I was seeing in the

00:00:34.520 --> 00:00:37.750
spirit, for

00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:39.069
the people who didn't watch it or

00:00:39.069 --> 00:00:39.079
are

00:00:39.079 --> 00:00:43.029
new here. I'm going to be

00:00:43.039 --> 00:00:47.350
praying over the elections and

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:48.990
just whatever the Lord puts on my heart.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.750
As I pray, He just said, 'Brandon, I want

00:00:50.760 --> 00:00:53.709
you to do 30 days of prayer videos up

00:00:53.719 --> 00:00:54.630
until the

00:00:54.630 --> 00:00:54.640
election.'Even

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:57.510
after, I believe we'll pray

00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:59.349
even after. There are some things that I'm

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:01.910
seeing in the spirit that will have

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:04.750
to be prayed even after the election is

00:01:04.760 --> 00:01:09.950
over, from what I've seen.

00:01:09.960 --> 00:01:12.390
It just takes work, but I appreciate you

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:15.230
all who want to work with me.

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.469
Okay, so this is what the Lord showed me

00:01:17.479 --> 00:01:21.749
yesterday. I saw a pipeline, like you

00:01:21.759 --> 00:01:25.350
see at a dam. It was a metal pipeline

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:27.270
that

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.469
water was running

00:01:29.479 --> 00:01:32.749
through; a river, a stream was flowing

00:01:32.759 --> 00:01:35.550
through this brook,

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:37.749
flowing through this pipeline. But there

00:01:37.759 --> 00:01:38.830
were

00:01:38.840 --> 00:01:43.749
demonic blockages in people's lives

00:01:43.759 --> 00:01:46.190
that were like tree limbs and rocks, and

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:47.550
they were the

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:52.550
blackest, like onyx-looking color.

00:01:54.360 --> 00:01:57.670
The darkest of the evil was trying

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:00.749
to block the river from

00:02:00.749 --> 00:02:00.759
flowing

00:02:00.759 --> 00:02:03.429
freely. Whenever I

00:02:03.439 --> 00:02:05.469
was standing up on the bank in the

00:02:05.479 --> 00:02:08.190
spirit, looking over

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:10.550
this brook, the Lord said,

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:14.110
'Take authority over those

00:02:14.110 --> 00:02:14.120
blockages.'That's

00:02:14.120 --> 00:02:15.470
what I was praying over.

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:16.750
When I was praying

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:18.710
in the spirit, I could

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:21.589
see those tree limbs

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:23.270
and the rocks, and they had

00:02:23.270 --> 00:02:23.280
yellow-looking

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:26.270
cat eyes that were bright,

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:29.509
neon yellow—a dark yellow,

00:02:29.519 --> 00:02:30.350
though.

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:32.350
They had a black center

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:34.470
inside of the

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:36.670
eye, and they were looking up at me on

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:38.790
the bank, kind of like a serpent would

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:42.470
look up. It was watching, trying to

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:45.190
remain disguised as they had a dam

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:47.509
trying to block up the flow of the Holy

00:02:47.519 --> 00:02:50.350
Spirit in some

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:53.910
people, trying to hinder them.

00:02:53.920 --> 00:02:55.229
That's what part of the

00:02:55.239 --> 00:02:56.710
intercessory prayer that we were praying

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:58.710
for yesterday was for—spiritual blockages

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:01.190
to be

00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:04.030
released from the people that

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:06.550
are praying with us. Even me,

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:09.190
I'll yield to the Holy Spirit.

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:11.949
I want a free flow.

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:17.350
I want more of Him and

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:19.710
less of me. We have this treasure in

00:03:19.710 --> 00:03:19.720
earthen

00:03:19.720 --> 00:03:21.470
vessels, that the excellency

00:03:21.470 --> 00:03:21.480
of

00:03:21.480 --> 00:03:23.309
the power will be known of Him and not

00:03:23.319 --> 00:03:25.789
of us. I'm telling you all, we're

00:03:25.799 --> 00:03:28.270
in a time like we've never seen before.

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:30.429
Part of what I saw yesterday

00:03:30.429 --> 00:03:30.439
was

00:03:30.439 --> 00:03:33.190
the Lord warning me about

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:38.030
big gatherings again. I was sent

00:03:38.040 --> 00:03:40.750
an email and even a text from a friend

00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:43.309
telling me, 'Hey, do you remember praying

00:03:43.319 --> 00:03:46.030
over

00:03:46.030 --> 00:03:46.040
Coachella?'I've

00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:47.949
been

00:03:47.959 --> 00:03:49.990
praying over Coachella, and the Lord will

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.149
show me

00:03:52.149 --> 00:03:52.159
things

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:56.869
way in advance over events trying to

00:03:56.879 --> 00:03:59.429
manifest, taking authority over them

00:03:59.429 --> 00:03:59.439
so

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:01.350
they don't happen.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:04.589
I saw mass shootings

00:04:04.589 --> 00:04:04.599
events

00:04:04.599 --> 00:04:07.270
happening at Coachella, and the Lord said,

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:11.110
'I want you to pray over this event

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:14.229
that this does not take

00:04:14.229 --> 00:04:14.239
place.'I

00:04:14.239 --> 00:04:16.390
thought it was the concert event, and

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:18.670
maybe it was; I don't know.

00:04:18.680 --> 00:04:20.310
We hear in part and see in

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:22.550
part. When you're looking

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:23.990
through the filter of what the

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.670
Lord's trying to tell you, you just keep

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:28.030
praying. I saw

00:04:28.030 --> 00:04:28.040
that

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.430
dam and what the Lord was warning me

00:04:29.440 --> 00:04:31.909
about back

00:04:31.909 --> 00:04:31.919
in

00:04:31.919 --> 00:04:33.990
March

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:36.830
of last year, and the Lord told me

00:04:36.840 --> 00:04:38.469
to start praying over this, that this was

00:04:38.479 --> 00:04:42.230
a serious thing to pray over. Well, my

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.590
friend sent me a text and said, 'Hey,

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:47.909
Brandon, did you see that President Donald

00:04:47.909 --> 00:04:47.919
Trump

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:51.110
was going to Coachella to

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:53.950
hold a rally

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:57.029
there?'I

00:04:57.039 --> 00:05:00.629
had no idea. The things that you get

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:02.870
in the spirit are warnings, and you

00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:05.430
try to put your own mind to it and

00:05:05.440 --> 00:05:07.029
get in trouble because you're thinking

00:05:07.039 --> 00:05:08.590
it's the concert. All I

00:05:08.590 --> 00:05:08.600
know is

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.230
that we

00:05:10.230 --> 00:05:10.240
pray. Whether

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:12.510
it could be

00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:16.670
the

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:18.270
presidential thing

00:05:18.270 --> 00:05:18.280
happening

00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:20.510
this weekend with the

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:24.029
speech, I don't know.

00:05:24.039 --> 00:05:26.070
All I know is the Lord warned

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:27.990
me to pray over this stuff.

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:29.950
Did it witness with me that this

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:33.230
could be it? Yeah, I thought

00:05:33.230 --> 00:05:33.240
it's

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:36.350
more than likely

00:05:36.350 --> 00:05:36.360
it.

00:05:36.360 --> 00:05:37.150
I don't want to get in the

00:05:37.160 --> 00:05:39.029
flesh about it, but I'm being real.

00:05:39.039 --> 00:05:41.270
There are certain

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:44.870
things I know about October—to pray

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:47.390
hedges of protection over

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:50.270
President Trump, praying that there is no

00:05:50.280 --> 00:05:52.309
weapon formed against him that would

00:05:52.319 --> 00:05:55.189
prosper, or the bystanders, the people

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:57.950
in the crowd. We

00:05:57.950 --> 00:05:57.960
pray that

00:05:57.960 --> 00:06:00.590
all

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:03.150
hidden things be revealed and that the

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:05.909
enemy would not have any kind of open

00:06:05.919 --> 00:06:08.469
door for opportunity to rob anybody's

00:06:08.479 --> 00:06:11.110
life.

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:14.390
Then the Lord showed me stadiums

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:16.830
again. When I was praying

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:19.710
yesterday, I saw the

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:22.189
stadiums again and I kept seeing New

00:06:22.199 --> 00:06:23.990
York. I was praying over New York in

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.909
these playoff games and the things

00:06:25.919 --> 00:06:28.589
happening with baseball.

00:06:28.599 --> 00:06:30.950
I don't want to go into a lot of that,

00:06:33.919 --> 00:06:36.710
but I'm praying over the open

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:38.550
stadiums. I told you about drones and

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.390
things like that; remember I warned you

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.029
all about that? I had my son make

00:06:42.039 --> 00:06:44.309
a short about it, and YouTube flagged it

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:48.270
and made me alter some things.

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:50.230
Whatever, it's their

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:53.990
platform. I just want to tell you all,

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.189
we are making a difference. I

00:06:56.199 --> 00:06:58.589
believe we've had over

00:06:58.589 --> 00:06:58.599
20,000

00:06:58.599 --> 00:07:01.070
people

00:07:01.070 --> 00:07:01.080
pray

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:04.070
with me in that last video. I'm

00:07:08.479 --> 00:07:10.830
excited that you

00:07:10.840 --> 00:07:12.510
want to pray with me. I don't want

00:07:12.520 --> 00:07:14.189
to keep rambling;

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:18.189
I just have some

00:07:18.199 --> 00:07:19.390
things in my heart before I

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:22.749
start praying.

00:07:22.759 --> 00:07:25.390
It's exciting that

00:07:27.479 --> 00:07:30.350
we are joining together as

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:32.430
an army and fighting off the

00:07:32.440 --> 00:07:35.589
wicked. I could feel

00:07:35.599 --> 00:07:38.189
the push against the darkness when

00:07:38.199 --> 00:07:40.430
we were praying and the video was going

00:07:40.440 --> 00:07:42.950
forth throughout the whole world. When

00:07:42.960 --> 00:07:44.390
you have

00:07:44.400 --> 00:07:47.149
20,000 people praying—whether

00:07:47.149 --> 00:07:47.159
it's

00:07:47.159 --> 00:07:48.710
five minutes

00:07:48.710 --> 00:07:48.720
or

00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:50.189
the whole

00:07:52.270 --> 00:07:52.280
thing—it's

00:07:54.280 --> 00:07:56.390
like an auditorium or a huge

00:07:56.400 --> 00:07:58.510
stadium full of people praying in the

00:07:58.520 --> 00:08:01.390
spirit, asking the Father for

00:08:01.400 --> 00:08:05.029
His angelic protection and

00:08:05.039 --> 00:08:07.070
manifestation of

00:08:07.080 --> 00:08:09.869
glory. When we pray

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:12.309
together

00:08:12.319 --> 00:08:14.869
as a family, we're able to

00:08:14.879 --> 00:08:18.070
do great things together.

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:19.869
I

00:08:19.879 --> 00:08:22.070
want

00:08:22.080 --> 00:08:24.550
to take a moment and just give God

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:27.230
thanks for what He's doing in

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:30.189
these last days on a YouTube channel,

00:08:30.199 --> 00:08:32.149
that we have power and authority over

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:34.230
the devil. We're seated with Him in the

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:36.469
heavenlies, far above all principalities,

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:38.709
powers, and might.

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:40.949
I was

00:08:40.959 --> 00:08:43.790
listening to a revival; we were going

00:08:43.800 --> 00:08:45.790
to church and there is a healing

00:08:45.800 --> 00:08:47.509
revival going on right

00:08:47.519 --> 00:08:49.949
now. She was talking about

00:08:49.959 --> 00:08:53.070
renewing your mind

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:55.590
to the Word of God on a day-to-day

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:58.310
basis because as soon as you get free,

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:00.790
the enemy comes immediately to steal

00:09:00.800 --> 00:09:03.430
the Word. He tries to steal the testimony

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:04.949
of your healing

00:09:04.949 --> 00:09:04.959
or

00:09:04.959 --> 00:09:06.790
whatever you've been

00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:08.470
believing for. You get your breakthrough

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:09.990
and the enemy's already right there

00:09:09.990 --> 00:09:10.000
trying

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:12.030
to take it from you.

00:09:12.040 --> 00:09:13.990
The only way you're able to stand

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:16.350
against the devil is by the Word of God.

00:09:16.360 --> 00:09:18.430
It is the Sword of the Spirit and

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:20.550
the Shield of Faith that

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:22.470
quenches all the fiery darts of the

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:25.110
wicked.

00:09:26.959 --> 00:09:29.470
You

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:31.110
need to have your sword and your shield

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:32.910
up, ready to fight it off. The Sword

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:35.389
of the Spirit is the Word of Faith,

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:44.389
and standing in faith

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:46.470
quenches

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:48.949
those fiery darts. I just want to

00:09:48.959 --> 00:09:50.430
encourage

00:09:50.440 --> 00:09:54.269
you that we're

00:09:54.279 --> 00:09:57.670
not armorless, we're not defeated, and we're

00:09:57.680 --> 00:09:59.990
not broke, busted, and disgusted.

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.150
The Greater One lives on the inside of

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:04.509
you, but you have to get a revelation

00:10:04.519 --> 00:10:06.430
knowledge of the Word of God inside of

00:10:06.440 --> 00:10:08.710
you. It's not like

00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:08.720
reading

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:11.470
a passage of scripture

00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:13.990
one time and

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:15.790
bypassing

00:10:15.790 --> 00:10:15.800
it.

00:10:15.800 --> 00:10:17.990
Faith cometh

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:20.550
by hearing and hearing by

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:23.069
the Word of God. If ye abide in

00:10:23.079 --> 00:10:26.470
Me and My words remain in you, you shall

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:29.670
ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:32.790
Dissect

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:36.470
that: if you abide in Him and

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:40.230
His words, the Bible, remain in you, you

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:42.670
shall ask what you will

00:10:42.670 --> 00:10:42.680
and

00:10:42.680 --> 00:10:46.389
it will be done. That's

00:10:46.399 --> 00:10:48.030
how your prayers are going to get

00:10:48.040 --> 00:10:50.710
answered in these last days.

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:53.269
If

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:55.310
your prayers aren't getting answered and

00:10:56.959 --> 00:10:59.590
you don't see results, check

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:02.150
your Word level. Check what you're

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:03.870
meditating on.

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:09.030
The more you meditate on the

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:11.629
Word and renew your mind,

00:11:11.639 --> 00:11:14.030
the more that Word gets down inside

00:11:14.040 --> 00:11:16.949
of you and becomes a rhema word, not

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:18.670
just reading scripture.

00:11:20.240 --> 00:11:23.910
I did that, and the

00:11:23.920 --> 00:11:26.509
Lord asked me, 'Now, what did you

00:11:26.509 --> 00:11:26.519
learn?'I

00:11:26.519 --> 00:11:29.269
said, 'I don't know if I

00:11:29.279 --> 00:11:30.949
learned anything.'He said, 'Then what

00:11:30.959 --> 00:11:33.389
good did it do you?'You have to understand the Word; you

00:11:33.399 --> 00:11:35.269
shall

00:11:35.279 --> 00:11:37.790
know the truth, and

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:40.550
the truth will set you free.

00:11:40.560 --> 00:11:42.190
You're wasting your time if you're just

00:11:42.200 --> 00:11:43.389
reading and

00:11:43.389 --> 00:11:43.399
getting nothing

00:11:43.399 --> 00:11:46.790
from it. Find just a couple

00:11:46.790 --> 00:11:46.800
of

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:49.550
scriptures and

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:52.030
meditate on them all day

00:11:52.040 --> 00:11:54.710
long until they get down inside of your

00:11:54.720 --> 00:11:57.949
spirit and become real to you.

00:11:57.959 --> 00:12:00.829
'Greater is He that is in me than he that

00:12:00.839 --> 00:12:04.030
is in the

00:12:04.040 --> 00:12:06.590
world.'Find

00:12:06.600 --> 00:12:08.389
those scriptures and write them on

00:12:08.399 --> 00:12:10.629
flashcards.

00:12:15.880 --> 00:12:18.910
Write it down, make it plain.

00:12:18.910 --> 00:12:18.920
Whenever

00:12:18.920 --> 00:12:21.310
you have a

00:12:21.320 --> 00:12:23.509
break at work, pull out

00:12:23.519 --> 00:12:25.829
that flashcard.

00:12:25.829 --> 00:12:25.839
Put

00:12:25.839 --> 00:12:28.069
it on

